text:
郑志勋轻笑一声，漫不经心将遥控器推到最高档。 震动频率骤然增加，跳蛋顶到身体最深处的敏感点。
没有情感的死物自然感受不到被它所折磨的人的崩溃，只是坚决地执行着命令，在肉穴敏感点上不停地刺激，挣扎着要向更深处探去。
柳岷析口中呻吟出声，脚一软要，眼看双膝要落地，郑志勋眼疾手快一把扶住了他的腰，他才没有直接倒在地上。
trans:
Zheng Zhixun let out a light laugh and absently pushed the remote control to the highest gear. The frequency of the vibrations suddenly increased, and the love egg pushed against the deepest sensitive point of the body.
The emotionless thing naturally couldn't feel the collapse of the person it was tormenting, and it just resolutely carried out its orders, struggling to probe deeper as it kept stimulating on the sensitive point of the anus.
Liu Minxi let out a soft moan as his legs gave way, and he was about to collapse to the ground. Quick as a flash, Zheng Zhixun caught him by the waist, preventing him from falling.
